title: Steve Bannon
added: In August 2020, Bannon was arrested and he and three others were charged with conspiracy to commit [[mail fraud]] and [[money laundering]] in connection to the [[We Build The Wall]] campaign. He has pleaded not guilty and will stand trial in May 2021.<ref>{{Cite news|last=Jacobs|first=Shayna|title=Steve Bannon’s trial set for May in border wall conspiracy case|language=en-US|work=Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/steve-bannon-trial-date/2020/08/31/a4c61e7c-eb90-11ea-ab4e-581edb849379_story.html|access-date=2020-09-01|issn=0190-8286}}</ref>
